Uh-huh. Okay.

35
00:03:11,233 --> 00:03:12,525
So?

36
00:03:12,609 --> 00:03:15,028
I agree with Dr. Saxon
and the medical team.

37
00:03:15,112 --> 00:03:17,072
We should reduce air travel
to once a week.

38
00:03:17,155 --> 00:03:18,741
I'm afraid that's not possible.

39
00:03:18,824 --> 00:03:21,243
You wanted a second opinion, sir.
You have it.

40
00:03:21,326 --> 00:03:23,726
I didn't want a second opinion.
I wanted a different opinion.

41
00:03:23,787 --> 00:03:25,247
Planes take a toll.

42
